WEBVTT

00:00:03.630 --> 00:00:06.870
KALETET MISPAR ARBA, Lev Rozov.

00:00:07.757 --> 00:00:13.420
 ir hot bakumen, m'hot aykh geshribn az s'iz keyner nisht ibergeblibn.

00:00:12.690 --> 00:00:14.620
ikh vel aykh zogn...

00:00:16.313 --> 00:00:19.684
mir zaynen gekumen, ikh bin gekumen in Dokshits

00:00:19.684 --> 00:00:21.670
nokh eyder ikh hob zikh bafrayt.

00:00:22.185 --> 00:00:26.721
hob ikh gezen, undzer eyn shtub iz geshtanen,

00:00:26.721 --> 00:00:28.794
nor gelebt hot dortn a krist.

00:00:29.728 --> 00:00:34.040
iz geven di shtot in gantsn farbrent.

00:00:36.495 --> 00:00:42.580
iz az ikh bin gekumen, bin ikh avekgegangen kukn vu di froy's eltern hobn ⟨ge- di⟩ froy's muter ⟨hot gelebt⟩.

00:00:42.580 --> 00:00:46.617
iz dortn zeyer shtub iz geven, iz geven shoyn a gesheft bay zey in shtub,

00:00:46.617 --> 00:00:50.220
opgeremontirt, vayl s'iz geven a gemoyerte shtub,

00:00:50.220 --> 00:00:52.140
hot zi nit geven farbrent.

00:00:52.140 --> 00:00:56.351
un ale hobn oyf mir gekukt: fun vanet nem ikh zikh?

00:00:58.399 --> 00:01:00.740
"yidn? s'iz do yidn?"

00:01:00.998 --> 00:01:04.070
mentshn hobn gekukt az s'iz nokh geblibn yidn.

00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:05.580
yidn. nokh, ikh'l aykh dertseyln.

00:01:05.580 --> 00:01:08.510
"s'iz do yidn UNK? un du,

00:01:08.510 --> 00:01:14.630
s'iz geven dayne a karte," zogn zey, "iz gevezn, un m'hot dir gezukht, di daytshn."

00:01:15.662 --> 00:01:20.089
vu bin ikh gevezn? zey, zaynen zey, zey zaynen nit geven in gantsn...

00:01:20.089 --> 00:01:24.431
un tsu mir in shtub zaynen gekumen tsu geyn di vos konen mir shoyn, poyerim.

00:01:24.758 --> 00:01:26.476
zogn zey, ⟨z-⟩...

00:01:26.476 --> 00:01:27.806
"du bist⟨,⟩ do?"

00:01:28.690 --> 00:01:32.635
un zey hobn mir ongehoybn dertseyln vi m'hot geharget, vi m'hot gefirt.

00:01:32.635 --> 00:01:34.348
ir farshteyt di zakh.

00:01:34.348 --> 00:01:38.252
hob ikh mit zey keyn gesheftn nit gefirt. ikh hob zey geheysn geyn.

00:01:38.713 --> 00:01:43.921
far mir hobn zey nokh a bisl yo moyre gehat, vayl s'iz dokh geven SOVETSKAYA VLAST' az ikh bin gekumen.

00:01:44.721 --> 00:01:48.512
zog ikh, zey hobn mir dertseylt ale zakhn.

00:01:49.463 --> 00:01:53.389
der partizan vos iz gevezn, der Yoshke Shapiro,

00:01:53.412 --> 00:01:59.661
iz er geven mayner, mayner, mayner ⟨a sakh...⟩ er iz geven der ershter vos kh'hob im ongezen, ⟨UNK⟩t oyfn veg.

00:01:59.661 --> 00:02:02.190
er iz geven do in land, nor er iz geshtorbn. er iz geven

00:02:02.190 --> 00:02:04.010
fun mayn yor, di zelbe zakh.

00:02:04.144 --> 00:02:05.538
mir zaynen beyde geven.

00:02:05.848 --> 00:02:09.740
zogt er tsu mir, "bay dir iz geven a yingele umgelofn...

00:02:21.424 --> 00:02:22.818
un dayn f-...

00:02:37.168 --> 00:02:40.390
un dayn froy iz geven ⟨m- mi-⟩...

00:02:44.003 --> 00:02:46.747
dayn froy iz geven mit undz in geto

00:02:46.855 --> 00:02:48.283
in eyn shtub."

00:02:48.306 --> 00:02:53.632
⟨hot⟩ ongehoybn zogn, "bay ⟨Kishenkovn⟩..." ir veyst nit, nor v- er hot mir ongehoybn zogn vu.

00:02:54.010 --> 00:02:58.948
"un der yingele iz bay dir shoyn umgelofn," zogt er, "a shvartsinker un zeyer a fayner."

00:03:03.848 --> 00:03:06.997
un zeyer mishpokhe hot men tsugenumen di letste,

00:03:07.611 --> 00:03:08.870
zogt er.

00:03:10.066 --> 00:03:11.960
zeyer mishpokhe.

00:03:12.859 --> 00:03:15.772
der bruder iz geshtorbn frier.

00:03:15.950 --> 00:03:19.380
far vos? er hot gekhapt a harts-atak UNK

00:03:19.380 --> 00:03:24.160
er iz geven dortn der UNK fun Kern-Kayemes. er iz geven a,

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:27.669
er iz geven a shtarker tsienist. dos iz der shvoger mayner.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:38.588
iz im hot men, er iz geshtorbn, nit ge- nit dervart di, di ge- er iz geven in geto, geshtorbn. ⟨der hot mir⟩ gezogt vi er hot im geholfn. er dertseylt mir

00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:42.380
azetike frages; er hot mir dertseylt zakhn, vi s'iz gevezn.

00:03:42.380 --> 00:03:44.336
er volt zey helfn mitn esn,

00:03:44.336 --> 00:03:47.250
brengen. s'iz dokh in geto oykh geven

00:03:47.250 --> 00:03:50.450
problemen; s'iz nit geven vos tsu esn. ⟨s'iz⟩ geven pr-...

00:03:50.450 --> 00:03:52.920
un der hoypt in di kleyne shtetlekh.

00:03:53.241 --> 00:03:56.002
s'iz nit geven keyn groyse farbindungen.

00:03:56.093 --> 00:03:58.837
dos hot er mir dertseylt fun mayn mishpokhe,

00:03:59.164 --> 00:04:00.848
Yoshke Shapiro.

00:04:00.848 --> 00:04:08.130
er iz, er hot gelebt in undzer gas, nor vayt fun mir, nor ikh bin mit im tsuzamen tsum priziv gegangen. mir zaynen geven fun eyn yor, fun zibetn.

00:04:08.130 --> 00:04:09.986
er iz oykh geven fun zibetn yor.

00:04:09.986 --> 00:04:14.272
⟨hot er⟩ gehat tate-mame mit, zey hobn, zeyere hot men alemen oysgeharget.

00:04:14.272 --> 00:04:16.601
eyn shvester iz geven in Erets-Yisroel,

00:04:16.601 --> 00:04:21.510
hob ikh ir shoyn, hobn mir dokh do mit ir ge- ikh hob d- ikh hob do a bild; ikh hob zikh mit zey getrofn.

00:04:21.510 --> 00:04:23.588
ale, ikh bin gekumen in land, hob ikh dokh

00:04:23.588 --> 00:04:26.917
alemen gekont zen. ir man hob ikh gekont gut,

00:04:27.514 --> 00:04:28.723
UNK man.

00:04:28.881 --> 00:04:32.548
un dos iz geven di lage, di ershte lage.

00:04:32.548 --> 00:04:36.680
shtot iz geven, vu yidn zaynen geven iz geven alts opgebrent.

00:04:36.964 --> 00:04:39.247
keyn yidishe ho⟨UNK⟩ nit geven.

00:04:39.247 --> 00:04:42.411
er hot mir gezogt vu di geto, di geto iz geven ammerstns

00:04:42.411 --> 00:04:45.710
bayn shul-hoyf, iz geven di geto.

00:04:47.190 --> 00:04:52.440
bay di shul-hoyf. di shuln zaynen ale farbrente geven, nit geblibn keyn eyne nit.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:54.423
alts iz geven farbrent.

00:04:54.548 --> 00:04:59.902
un der, der beys-seyfer⟨, s'iz, m'hot⟩ alts, alts iz geven farbrent, vayl alts iz geven hiltserne.

00:04:59.902 --> 00:05:03.345
geblibn bay undz in gas, eyne iz geven a tsvey-shtokike

00:05:03.345 --> 00:05:05.060
gemoyerte shtub

00:05:05.061 --> 00:05:08.470
iz geblibn. geblibn di shtub fun mayn froy

00:05:08.470 --> 00:05:11.285
iz geblibn, di shtub fun ire eltern,

00:05:11.285 --> 00:05:15.820
un nokh eyne iz geven a gemoyerte shtub ⟨vu eyner hot gelebt⟩ UNK

00:05:14.882 --> 00:05:16.840
vi lang zent ir geblibn in...?

00:05:15.820 --> 00:05:17.630
der apteyker. v-...?

00:05:16.928 --> 00:05:20.620
ir zent gef- geforn aleyn keyn Do⟨b⟩shi- ⟨k-⟩ Dokshits?

00:05:18.900 --> 00:05:20.660
aleyn. aleyn.

00:05:20.699 --> 00:05:21.514
aleyn.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.490
aleyn.

00:05:21.514 --> 00:05:23.680
vi lang zent ir geblibn ⟨do-⟩...?

00:05:22.490 --> 00:05:25.050
un nokh dem hob ikh dokh umgekert krik ahin;

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:27.043
dortn zaynen geven di eltern mayne.

00:05:27.218 --> 00:05:29.870
dernokh dem iz avekgeforn shoyn,

00:05:29.870 --> 00:05:33.310
az Vilne hot men farnumen shoyn un der daytsh iz geven UNK,

00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:35.480
gegangen, m'iz gegangen oyf Berlin,

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:38.957
iz avekgeforn di tokh- di shvester...

00:05:39.570 --> 00:05:44.220
zi iz geshtorbn UNK shvester. zi iz f- far dray geshtorbn...

00:05:44.220 --> 00:05:46.370
yene shvester mitn foter,

00:05:46.810 --> 00:05:48.250
di ershte.

00:05:48.885 --> 00:05:54.010
yene shve- un di muter iz nokh geven alts dortn vi di kinder, ale dortn geven.

00:05:54.994 --> 00:05:56.743
UNK

00:05:56.750 --> 00:06:01.570
⟨zi iz⟩ gekumen aheym, hot zi UNK vos hot zi geton? opgereynikt di hoyz,

00:06:01.570 --> 00:06:05.470
aroysgetribn di velkhe hobn dortn gelebt,

00:06:06.385 --> 00:06:12.364
un gemakht a bisl ordenung. di partizaner hobn zey geholfn. dortn hobn gelebt lebn undz, di tsveyte

00:06:12.364 --> 00:06:16.296
shtub vos iz geblibn, a polyak hot gelebt; er iz geven shoyn geshtorbn, iz keyner nit geven.

00:06:16.296 --> 00:06:18.394
⟨zaynen⟩ dortn gelebt partizaner.

00:06:18.501 --> 00:06:20.925
di partizaner oykh, undzere khevre.

00:06:20.931 --> 00:06:25.903
iz eyner fun di partizaner geshtorbn, iz geblibn tsvey, zaynen avekgeforn in Amerike.

00:06:26.348 --> 00:06:31.821
eyne iz geven DVORA, a meydl, ⟨,⟩ zi hot zikh, mir forgeleygt, ikh zol mit zey forn.

00:06:31.821 --> 00:06:37.052
zog ikh, ⟨"ikh'l a-"⟩ bin okersht gekumen in zeks un fertsiktn yor, "vel ikh nit iberlozn di mishpokhe,

00:06:37.052 --> 00:06:39.420
un ikh'l forn in Erets-Yisroel."

00:06:39.870 --> 00:06:41.960
⟨z-⟩ zog ikh, "ikh for in Erets-Yisroel."

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:46.870
zi zogt, zi hot a shvester in Amerike, zey forn in Amerike. zog ikh, "dervayle for ikh ergets nit."

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:49.060
dos iz geven di, di sof.

00:06:48.850 --> 00:06:49.850
⟨un ve-...⟩

00:06:49.060 --> 00:06:53.471
zaynen mir geblibn arbetn, zaynen mir geblibn in Poy- in, Vilne

00:06:53.471 --> 00:06:54.506
tsen yor.

00:06:54.791 --> 00:06:58.350
iz ir zent g- tsurikgeforn mit di eltern keyn Vilne.

00:06:57.940 --> 00:07:01.210
 mi- di el-, di eltern zaynen shoyn geven,

00:07:00.724 --> 00:07:02.590
zenen shoyn geven in Vilne?

00:07:01.210 --> 00:07:03.930
geven in Dokshits

00:07:03.930 --> 00:07:08.220
un zaynen avekgeforn in Glubok, in an ander shtetl. far vos?

00:07:08.220 --> 00:07:10.790
vayle di, di shvester MANYA

00:07:10.790 --> 00:07:15.550
hot dortn gearbet a bukhhalter in VOENTORG, ikh veys, oykh gearbet bay di UNK

00:07:15.550 --> 00:07:16.899
bay di sovyetn.

00:07:16.922 --> 00:07:21.320
⟨i- iz az,⟩ me darf dokh zey SNABZHAEn; di eltern iz dokh nit...

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:22.900
hobn zey avekgeforn tsu dos.

00:07:22.900 --> 00:07:24.600
nor az di muter iz gekumen...

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:26.370
ikh vil aykh oto dos zogn kurts:

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:28.791
mir hobn gefunen di shtub un zi iz avek in feld

00:07:28.791 --> 00:07:33.020
vu es hodeven zikh un a ruf geton di ki, ⟨zaynen zey⟩ tsugelofn tsu ir.

00:07:33.814 --> 00:07:35.732
⟨hot zi ge-⟩ tsugenumen di ki

00:07:35.805 --> 00:07:39.890
ire. s'iz geven tsvey: eyne hot men, di partizaner zogn, me zol zi avek-

00:07:39.890 --> 00:07:42.090
avekgebn dem ver hot gehaltn.

00:07:42.117 --> 00:07:45.310
ir veyst dokh, m'hot nit gevolt mit di poyerim nokh onheybn zikh...

00:07:45.310 --> 00:07:48.185
hot tsugenumen di ki un alts un zey zaynen avekgeforn

00:07:48.428 --> 00:07:50.010
⟨a-⟩ in di tsveyte shtot.

00:07:48.745 --> 00:07:51.020
iz ir ze- ven hot ir khas-...?

00:07:50.010 --> 00:07:52.910
un ikh bin gekumen in zeks un fertsiktn,

00:07:52.910 --> 00:07:55.280
bin ikh gekumen glaykh in Vilne.

00:07:55.212 --> 00:07:59.110
un v- vos hot ir getun in Vilne? in vos hot ir gearbet?

00:07:57.470 --> 00:08:03.160
⟨ikh,⟩ Vilne hob ikh gefunen oykh a shtot tsebrent.

00:08:03.227 --> 00:08:05.890
di geto iz geven leydik fun hayzer.

00:08:05.890 --> 00:08:10.522
ikh bin arayn dortn in geto un oysge- ⟨unt-⟩ farrikht a shtub ⟨un zikh,⟩

00:08:10.522 --> 00:08:14.060
gemakht di shtub, bin ikh arayngegangen lebn ahin mit di eltern.

00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:15.950
⟨m-⟩ mit, ⟨un⟩ ven hot ir khas-...?

00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:16.603
yidn zaynen nit geven.

00:08:16.710 --> 00:08:21.479
yugntlekhe... m'hot nokh geharget, iz dortn geven banditn nokh a sakh...

00:08:21.722 --> 00:08:25.030
mir zaynen ⟨gek-⟩ ale yugntlekhe fun di shtetlekh.

00:08:25.789 --> 00:08:27.318
fun di shtetlekh.

00:08:27.443 --> 00:08:31.532
der hoy- di shtot iz dokh shoyn nit geven Vilne keyn poylishe.

00:08:31.532 --> 00:08:37.020
iz zi, az mir zaynen gekumen iz zi shoyn geven a litvishe, di litvishe hoyptshtot.

00:08:37.990 --> 00:08:40.300
zi iz dokh nit geven keyn poylishe;

00:08:40.300 --> 00:08:42.270
zi iz geven di litvishe hoyptshtot.

00:08:42.477 --> 00:08:46.940
nu, zaynen mir ahin gekumen un mir hobn zikh ayngeordnt, di gantse mishpokhe.

00:08:46.940 --> 00:08:48.395
mir hobn genumen arbetn,

00:08:48.553 --> 00:08:52.827
der in an artel... vu hob ikh gearbet? avek in an artel a bisl tsayt.

00:08:48.710 --> 00:08:50.350
vos hot ir gear-...?

00:08:52.827 --> 00:09:00.520
ikh hob dernokh dem gearbet ⟨i-⟩ di letste arbet mayne iz geven in a, oyf di,...

00:09:00.520 --> 00:09:05.237
oyfn arkhiv. dos i- ikh bin avek azoy arbetn oyfn arkhiv,

00:09:05.412 --> 00:09:10.705
⟨,⟩ zaynen mir avekgegangen un mir hobn gearbet in VOENTORG. ikh bin avek fun, in DOM OFITSEROV

00:09:10.815 --> 00:09:12.570
di letste, oyfn arkhiv.

00:09:11.622 --> 00:09:13.630
ven hot ir khasene gehat?

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:16.250
khasene gehat hob ikh dokh for der... a! mit der froy?

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:16.720
yo.

00:09:16.250 --> 00:09:18.980
in zeks un fertsiktn yor iz gekumen di f-

00:09:18.980 --> 00:09:21.640
gekumen oykh azetike getrofene vos...

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:24.713
⟨hob ikh⟩ zikh mit ir getrofn bay ire frayn⟨t⟩, oykh fun,

00:09:24.713 --> 00:09:26.110
fun undzer shtetl.

00:09:26.110 --> 00:09:29.380
getrofn, hob ikh a kuk get⟨UNK⟩... un zi iz aley-....

00:09:28.460 --> 00:09:30.550
in zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:09:29.380 --> 00:09:31.160
in zeks un fertsiktn yor.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:34.280
zeks un fertsik hob ikh zikh mit ir getrofn. zi iz geven a bukhhalter

00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:35.880
un zi hot gearbet

00:09:35.888 --> 00:09:38.040
oyf a, oyfn ban-arbet.

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:41.000
zog ikh, "loz dortn op di arbet un kum in Vilne.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:44.230
kum in Vilne, veln mir zikh aynordenen." keyn khasenes hot men...

00:09:43.347 --> 00:09:45.383
un vi h- vi heyst di froy?

00:09:44.930 --> 00:09:46.310
di froy? BELLA.

00:09:46.418 --> 00:09:49.520
keyn khasenes ho⟨t men⟩ nit gemakht.

00:09:50.653 --> 00:09:52.180
un azoy lebn mir.

00:09:52.223 --> 00:09:53.910
farshribn UNK.

00:09:52.746 --> 00:09:55.457
vi lang zent ir geblibn in Vilne?

00:09:54.890 --> 00:09:57.307
in Vilne zaynen mir geblibn tsen yor.

00:09:57.425 --> 00:10:00.550
un vos iz gesh- ven zent ir gekumen keyn Erets-Yisroel?

00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:05.289
fun, in Vilne geblibn, zaynen geven tsen yor, un in fu- mir, aher zaynen mir gekumen,

00:10:05.289 --> 00:10:10.450
zaynen mir ongehoybn gebn papirn vi m'hot ⟨derhert⟩... dos iz dokh geven Stalin; vi Stalin iz avekgefaln

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:12.290
un s'iz gekumen KHRUSHCHЁV...

00:10:12.290 --> 00:10:15.034
dos iz al di polit⟨ish⟩e, politishe inyonim...

00:10:15.034 --> 00:10:18.150
gekumen KHRUSHCHЁV, hot men ongehoybn zogn az poylishe,

00:10:18.150 --> 00:10:21.495
ver s'iz geven⟨,⟩ poy-, poylishe birger konen aroysforn,

00:10:21.687 --> 00:10:23.790
hobn mir ongehoybn gebn papirn.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:27.130
ir zent geven farn krig poylishe birger.

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:31.580
poy-, zikher! ⟨a- mir zaynen dokh⟩ geven in poylishn militer un, un umetum UNK poylishe birger,

00:10:27.447 --> 00:10:28.447
yo.

00:10:31.580 --> 00:10:33.210
zaynen mir geven f⟨UNK⟩ militer.

00:10:33.210 --> 00:10:35.840
hobn mir ongehoybn gebn papirn az mir forn NA RODINU,

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:37.050
 forn...

00:10:35.862 --> 00:10:38.100
vu ahin hot ir gevolt forn?

00:10:37.930 --> 00:10:40.000
mir hobn in Erets-Yisroel gevolt forn.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:41.410
ir hot gevolt, ir hot gevust, ir...

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.452
mir hobn shoyn glaykh,

00:10:41.452 --> 00:10:45.790
glaykh dortn hobn mir shoyn gevust az di vos forn in Poyln forn in Erets-Yisroel.

00:10:45.790 --> 00:10:47.634
mir hobn shoyn gehat a farbindung.

00:10:47.995 --> 00:10:49.260
iz hob ikh gezogt...

00:10:49.260 --> 00:10:51.180
iz afile mayn froy,

00:10:51.180 --> 00:10:52.970
mayn froy un ir bruder

00:10:52.970 --> 00:10:57.130
hot ongehoybn zogn az er hot a shvester in Brazil, a raykhe, do...

00:10:57.130 --> 00:10:59.666
zog ikh, "ikh darf keynem's raykhkeyt nit."

00:10:59.925 --> 00:11:01.803
un der foter hot mir ongehoybn,

00:11:01.803 --> 00:11:04.053
"fir mir avek in Erets-Yisroel shtarbn."

00:11:05.055 --> 00:11:06.220
ir farshteyt?

00:11:06.220 --> 00:11:07.910
s'iz dokh nit geven a lebn!

00:11:07.910 --> 00:11:09.810
mir zaynen geven shvakh.

00:11:09.810 --> 00:11:11.599
ir, ir shtelt zikh for,

00:11:11.599 --> 00:11:16.000
vi mir, vi... ikh bin nit geven, nor vi di eltern hobn oysgezen.

00:11:16.193 --> 00:11:17.970
di muter hob ikh shoyn do in,

00:11:17.970 --> 00:11:20.900
in Vilne gemakht... do in Erets-Yisroel

00:11:20.900 --> 00:11:22.420
gemakht ir a NITUAKH.

00:11:22.420 --> 00:11:24.480
di muter iz geshtorbn fun DOM LEV,

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.290
un der foter hot derlebt biz nayntsik,

00:11:27.516 --> 00:11:30.700
nayntsik akht yor, biz hundert yor on tsvey yor.

00:11:30.773 --> 00:11:36.120
iz di foter un di muter zenen mitgekumen mit enk do aher keyn Erets-Yisroel?

00:11:33.750 --> 00:11:38.760
⟨mit u-⟩ gel- mir hobn zey afile nit gelozt oyf eyn tog. ikh'l aykh zogn,

00:11:38.760 --> 00:11:41.415
ikh hob zey gehaltn, ikh!

00:11:41.607 --> 00:11:44.780
nit gegebn di kinder, keynem; ikh bin...

00:11:44.780 --> 00:11:47.170
un mayn froy hot zey take tsugenumen.

00:11:47.170 --> 00:11:50.561
ikh hob g- bay mir iz dokh eyn, di kind iz geborn in Vilne.

00:11:50.740 --> 00:11:55.360
iz di eltste tokhter iz geboyrn in Vilne. un di tsveyte tokhter?

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:53.770
in Vilne.

00:11:53.770 --> 00:11:55.920
un di iz geborn in Erets-Yisroel.

00:11:55.380 --> 00:11:57.366
iz geboyrn shoyn in Erets-Yisroel.

00:11:56.330 --> 00:11:58.080
in Erets-Yisroel geborn.

00:11:57.366 --> 00:12:01.100
un ayer briders un shvesters zenen oykh gekumen do aher?

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:05.009
 di, UNK glaykh ale... neyn! ikh bin gekumen gor fun di eyn- der ershter,

00:12:01.770 --> 00:12:03.020
⟨ale t-⟩...

00:12:05.009 --> 00:12:08.760
nokh mir iz gekumen der bruder mitn foter mit di muter un di shvester,

00:12:08.760 --> 00:12:11.270
zaynen gekumen in dray monat arum UNK

00:12:10.345 --> 00:12:13.596
vi lang zent ir geven oyfn veg ⟨i⟩n Poyln?

00:12:13.770 --> 00:12:15.200
vu zaynen mir geven...?

00:12:14.262 --> 00:12:16.080
vi, in Poyln, vi...?

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:18.520
a! i-, vi zay- vu, a, fo- forndik in Erets-Yisroel?

00:12:17.960 --> 00:12:22.310
n- fun Vilne, zogt ir, zent ir ersht geforn keyn Poyln...

00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:22.100
 gekumen in Poyln.

00:12:22.100 --> 00:12:23.690
vu zaynen mir geven in Poyln?

00:12:23.690 --> 00:12:26.988
Poy- o! di poyl- oykh iz do a gantse, a gantse zakh.

00:12:26.988 --> 00:12:30.290
Poyln zaynen mir gekumen, zaynen mir geven in,

00:12:30.290 --> 00:12:34.064
in V- Vrotslaver OBLAST' in, ⟨Gzhitsk,⟩

00:12:34.071 --> 00:12:36.510
⟨in Zhitske⟩, a shtetl.

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:40.430
un dort hot ir gevart oyf di papirn keyn Erets-Yisroel.

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:41.610
un do, un ikh hob nokh, oto do bin ikh geven a,

00:12:41.610 --> 00:12:44.720
a, der predsyedatel fun a yidishe, yidishe,

00:12:43.988 --> 00:12:45.860
fun di yidishe gemeynde.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:46.454
f-, gemeynde,

00:12:46.454 --> 00:12:50.918
fun, s'iz dokh geven do a yidisher kultur-farband, hob ikh getrofn,

00:12:50.918 --> 00:12:52.639
nor vos? mir hobn gevolt,

00:12:52.639 --> 00:12:57.858
ikh bin geven bayn konsulat, bay dem yidishn. der konsulat iz gekumen tsu mir in shtub,

00:12:57.898 --> 00:12:59.380
mit der froy,

00:12:59.380 --> 00:13:03.070
un mir hobn dortn gemakht az m'hot tsuzamengeklibn di yidn

00:13:03.070 --> 00:13:06.464
vos zaynen gekumen un mir hobn a bisl tsu zey geredt.

00:13:06.606 --> 00:13:10.143
er hot gevust az ikh vil forn in Erets-Yisroel.

00:13:10.352 --> 00:13:15.460
hot er tsu zey geredt. un ikh bin geven der pre- der prezes fun der yidisher gemeynde do,

00:13:15.460 --> 00:13:17.000
fun der religyezer.

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:21.967
un ⟨ikh,⟩ mir hobn shoyn gefunen, gemakht a religyeze shul, der foter.

00:13:21.967 --> 00:13:27.170
un vi ⟨z-⟩ vi azoy brengt men di yidn tsu, az zey zoln kumen in eyn ort?

00:13:27.170 --> 00:13:29.220
me darf zey gebn esn.

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:34.060
kh'hob glaykh avekgeforn in Varshe. ikh bin geven in Varshe ⟨un genumen a erloybenish⟩

00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:36.200
oyf koylenen di beheymes,

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:38.350
me zol makhn yidishe STOLOVe,

00:13:38.350 --> 00:13:40.080
a koshere STOLOVe.

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:41.610
m'hot gemakht koshere esn,

00:13:41.610 --> 00:13:43.314
iz zaynen gevorn yidn.

00:13:43.314 --> 00:13:48.470
hob ikh ongeshribn oyf a tir az s'iz do a talmed-toyre; velkhe kinder veln kumen lernen

00:13:48.470 --> 00:13:49.830
in talmed-toyre,

00:13:48.750 --> 00:13:50.260
veln bakumen esn.

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:52.080
vet men krign esn. ershtns.

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:58.150
tsveytns, der bruder, ⟨d-⟩ der bruder mit nokh eyne a froy, iz gekumen ⟨i-⟩ fun Erets-Yisro- fun Poyln,

00:13:58.150 --> 00:14:01.073
vos zi iz a mol farblibn fun Erets-Yisroel,

00:14:01.551 --> 00:14:02.827
mit a zun.

00:14:03.238 --> 00:14:05.564
iz iz geblibn in Rusland farblibn.

00:14:05.564 --> 00:14:10.270
iz zi gekumen, hobn zey mitn bruder gemakht a shul un m'hot gelernt ivrit.

00:14:09.220 --> 00:14:10.380
ivrit.

00:14:10.270 --> 00:14:13.240
der bruder hot gekont, der bruder iz gekumen mit a shprakh.

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:15.010
der bruder iz gekumen aher,

00:14:15.010 --> 00:14:17.560
hot er gearbet in, MAS HAKHNASA.

00:14:16.873 --> 00:14:21.423
un vos hot ir gearbet ven ir zent gekumen do aher keyn Erets-Yisroel?

00:14:21.050 --> 00:14:24.630
in Erets-Yisroel hob ikh frier gearbet ale arbet,

00:14:24.630 --> 00:14:26.020
oykh oyf maleray.

00:14:26.020 --> 00:14:30.514
far vos? vayle dos iz geven a fardinst, a ⟨sakh, kh'hob ge- gezogt⟩ UNK...

00:14:30.514 --> 00:14:33.310
do iz do afile eyner a KHUDOZHNIK, oykh fun mayn shul,

00:14:33.310 --> 00:14:35.970
un eyner iz mit mir gekumen fun mayn,

00:14:35.970 --> 00:14:38.860
fun mayn shul, vos er hot z- mir hobn zikh gelernt tsuzamen.

00:14:38.860 --> 00:14:42.535
er iz a tseykhener oto do, arb- arbet er oyf, oyf di tsaytungen.

00:14:43.198 --> 00:14:54.260
zo-... a gra⟨f⟩irer iz er. iz, iz men gekumen, ikh hob zikh genumen arbetn oyf maleray. oyf maleray zogt mir di froy, ⟨d- az⟩ ikh hob opgearbet... okersht vi ikh bin gekumen, oyf morgn hot men shoyn mir gezukht.

00:14:54.260 --> 00:14:57.610
eyner iz gekumen a Vilner, hot er proklamirt mir,

00:14:57.610 --> 00:15:00.990
hot men gezukht... zogt di fr- hob ikh gebrakht fun a vokh fardinst,

00:15:00.990 --> 00:15:03.627
zogt zi, zogt zi, "mir veln dokh do zayn gvirim!"

00:15:03.904 --> 00:15:07.841
ir farshteyt? zi hot nit farshtanen; ⟨der esn hot gekost⟩ bilik,

00:15:07.841 --> 00:15:09.760
un ikh hob fa- un mir hot men getsolt

00:15:09.760 --> 00:15:14.070
tsen lires... dan iz dokh geven nokh lires... a tog,

00:15:14.070 --> 00:15:18.090
iz hot zi derzen az s'iz a kapital ⟨a- antkegn⟩ UNK.

00:15:18.090 --> 00:15:20.720
nu, iz do hob ikh gearbet a bisl,

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:22.840
nor ikh hob nit gevolt ⟨oyf dem arbetn⟩.

00:15:22.840 --> 00:15:26.050
ikh ho- ikh ⟨hob oyf di⟩ arbet nit gevolt arbetn.

00:15:26.050 --> 00:15:29.329
bin ikh gekumen, ikh hob zikh ayngeordnt arbet in papir-fabrik.

00:15:30.178 --> 00:15:32.720
dos iz di letste arbet mayne geven,

00:15:32.777 --> 00:15:36.420
papir-fabrik, hob ikh opgearbet tsvelf yor.

00:15:36.940 --> 00:15:40.810
ir zent haynt, haynt f- a frumer mentsh, ADON Rozov?

00:15:38.480 --> 00:15:42.940
un ikh hob g- un ikh bin geven dortn, ⟨gekrogn a JOB⟩.

00:15:43.959 --> 00:15:47.275
ir zent haynt a frume- a frumer mentsh, ADON Rozov?

00:15:47.050 --> 00:15:48.050
vo-...?

00:15:47.275 --> 00:15:49.420
do in Erets-Yisroel geyt ir in,

00:15:49.460 --> 00:15:52.640
in bes- in shil arayn? ir zent frum?

00:15:51.765 --> 00:15:55.210
a, a mol. neyn, UNK, ⟨ikh bin nit frum⟩.

00:15:55.190 --> 00:15:56.770
s'hot zikh geendert...

00:15:55.210 --> 00:15:58.060
vos vayter ikh leb, bin ikh nit frum.

00:15:58.715 --> 00:16:00.050
nit frum.

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:02.290
di, di milkhome...

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:02.170
ikh'l aykh zogn azoy:

00:16:02.170 --> 00:16:04.530
ikh bin a gleybiker yid shtark,

00:16:04.806 --> 00:16:06.943
nor ikh gleyb nit in rabonim.

00:16:09.210 --> 00:16:11.342
in di rabonim gleyb ikh nit.

00:16:11.342 --> 00:16:12.765
kh'hob gezen. i-

00:16:12.771 --> 00:16:16.899
ikh bin a mentsh aza vos ikh kon nit geyn vos ikh ze nit.

00:16:17.057 --> 00:16:18.227
kh'hob gezen.

00:16:18.227 --> 00:16:19.920
ikh gleyb in got

00:16:19.977 --> 00:16:23.250
un ikh bet got un er helft mir.

00:16:24.027 --> 00:16:26.063
un ikh darf keynem's

00:16:26.085 --> 00:16:29.268
protektsye tsu im, tsu got nit hobn,

00:16:29.494 --> 00:16:32.340
vayle got iz undzer alemen's.

00:16:33.308 --> 00:16:36.360
ir farshteyt? got iz undzer alemen's.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:39.574
yeder kon betn got, s'shteyt in der toyre,

00:16:39.574 --> 00:16:42.915
oyf vos far a shprakh er vil, er kon,

00:16:42.915 --> 00:16:44.524
un vi er kon betn.

00:16:45.053 --> 00:16:46.312
bet ikh,

00:16:46.690 --> 00:16:51.000
nor ⟨mit dos⟩, ikh gey in shul rosheshone, yomkiper gey ikh in shul.

00:16:51.250 --> 00:16:55.200
di milkhome, di, dos az ir hot farloyrn di mishpokhe,

00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:58.810
di krig hot geendert di,

00:16:58.530 --> 00:16:59.880
ikh'l, ikh'l...

00:16:59.230 --> 00:17:04.500
dos vos ir, ir zen- ir zent andersh gevorn nokhn krig, ir filt...?

00:17:03.190 --> 00:17:09.720
ikh'l aykh zo- nu, ikh'l aykh zogn azoy: ikh bin andersh gevorn nokh di tsveyte mol khasene hobn.

00:17:12.119 --> 00:17:14.745
ir farshteyt? ir farshteyt mir,

00:17:15.380 --> 00:17:18.500
kh'hob nit, ikh hob nit getrofn mit dem.

00:17:18.988 --> 00:17:22.720
shoyn dernokh... ikh hob mit dem nit ge- ir farshteyt mir.

00:17:22.887 --> 00:17:24.923
s'iz vegn dem nit tsu reydn.

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:28.520
⟨s'iz⟩ UNK nor... oto dos iz geven der lebn.

00:17:27.679 --> 00:17:30.781
s'iz do ETWAS vos ir hot g- ir volt gevolt zogn

00:17:30.781 --> 00:17:35.920
far ayer mishpokhe, di, far di yugnt haynt, vos me ken...?

00:17:31.980 --> 00:17:34.610
ikh hob zey ge-, i-

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:40.070
ikh hob gevolt UNK di ershte zakh hob ikh gevolt lernen di kinder. lernen.

00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:42.112
bay mir iz di e- di yingere tokhter,

00:17:42.112 --> 00:17:45.580
di yingere tokhter a inzhenyer. zi hot gekontshet, ⟨do⟩.

00:17:45.580 --> 00:17:48.280
nokh dem iz zi zikh avekgegangen lernen oyf a bukhhalter,

00:17:48.280 --> 00:17:51.343
un itster arbet zi... zi hot gemakht HORAA oykh,

00:17:51.343 --> 00:17:53.150
un zi volt zikh haynt oykh lernen,

00:17:53.150 --> 00:17:57.237
un zi, un zi arbet far a lerer fun matematike un MEKHASHVIM.

00:17:57.514 --> 00:17:59.660
zi iz a gerotene, oto di...

00:17:58.911 --> 00:18:00.600
un di eltere tekhter?

00:17:59.660 --> 00:18:02.970
un di eltere tokhter hobn mir nit gekont lernen,

00:18:02.970 --> 00:18:07.240
vayle mir zaynen geven okersht gekumen.

00:18:07.240 --> 00:18:10.647
mir hobn gedarft a dire, hobn mir genumen a mishkante,

00:18:10.647 --> 00:18:14.050
iz di eltere tokhter a krankn-shvester ⟨bay undz⟩.

00:18:13.002 --> 00:18:14.740
a krankn-shvester?

00:18:14.490 --> 00:18:16.478
a krankn-shvester. ir farshteyt,

00:18:16.478 --> 00:18:18.110
s'iz, s'iz a untersheyd:

00:18:18.110 --> 00:18:19.929
ikh, ikh hob alts,

00:18:19.929 --> 00:18:25.130
ikh aleyn hob dos nit gekont dergreykhn, vos ikh hob gevolt az di kinder zoln dergreykhn.

00:18:25.130 --> 00:18:27.780
oto mayne plimenikes tsvey, di tokhter's,

00:18:27.855 --> 00:18:29.924
eyn zun iz doktor FIZIKA,

00:18:30.842 --> 00:18:32.658
eyn zun ARKHITEKTOR,

00:18:32.783 --> 00:18:35.160
un zey zaynen groy-, groyse UNK...

00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:40.600
un bay dem bruder oykh, eyne arbet in a universitet in Yerusholaim, eyn kind.

00:18:40.697 --> 00:18:44.720
⟨bay⟩, mir zaynen a mishpo- ot dos iz a dank mir.

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:48.460
ikh hob, vil az me zol zikh lernen,

00:18:48.460 --> 00:18:51.450
derfar vos ikh hob dos nit gemakht,

00:18:51.450 --> 00:18:54.461
un ikh hob nit gehat keyn meglekhkeyt dos tsu makhn.

00:18:55.007 --> 00:18:58.286
ikh bin geborn gevorn in a shverer tsayt,

00:18:58.286 --> 00:19:00.412
fun der ershter velt-milkhome,

00:19:00.412 --> 00:19:03.030
untergevaksn, tsveyte velt-milkhome,

00:19:03.030 --> 00:19:04.774
un ikh hob alts gelitn,

00:19:04.774 --> 00:19:06.940
un gehat oyf zikh a mishpokhe.

00:19:08.018 --> 00:19:09.990
ot dos iz geven, vi ikh zog...

00:19:09.638 --> 00:19:12.800
ir klert, ir klert oft iber di mishpokhe,

00:19:12.320 --> 00:19:13.330
i-...

00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:15.960
iber di milkhome, iber vos s'iz geven?

00:19:14.610 --> 00:19:19.481
nu, ot dos iz mayn gants, itster iz di gedanken mayne in gantsn andere,

00:19:19.481 --> 00:19:21.725
nor danken got ikh hob derlebt

00:19:21.725 --> 00:19:25.830
zakhn gute. ikh ze oyf di kinder, ikh hob geholfn koyfn di kinder,

00:19:25.830 --> 00:19:27.243
eyner a shtub.

00:19:27.243 --> 00:19:30.690
de- der elterer hob ikh gekoyft a shtub; ikh hob nokh gehat m⟨eglekh-...⟩

00:19:30.690 --> 00:19:33.594
mir hobn beyde gearbet UNK zi un ikh.

00:19:35.068 --> 00:19:39.686
un ikh hob gekrogn a harts-atak az mir iz geven fir un zekhtsik yor.

00:19:40.435 --> 00:19:44.850
dos iz alts, shpilt zikh opet vos do, vos me hot gelebt.

00:19:45.261 --> 00:19:49.750
un ikh bin shoyn tsvey un tsvantsik UNK yor krank oyfn hartsn.

00:19:49.750 --> 00:19:52.800
haynt ⟨hot⟩ mir in der fri gekhapt di harts, hob ikh gemeynt

00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:55.910
az ikh... ikh bin nervez geven dray teg,

00:19:55.910 --> 00:19:58.290
az mir hot get⟨UNK⟩ di harts, vayle ikh hob,

00:19:58.290 --> 00:20:02.910
kh'hob... ikh'l⟨,⟩ zogn aykh dem emes: keyn helft aykh nit dertseylt,

00:20:02.910 --> 00:20:05.350
nor s'iz genug vifl ikh hob dertseylt.

00:20:05.350 --> 00:20:07.400
far mir iz dos shver.

00:20:07.550 --> 00:20:10.080
kh'bin shoyn alt bay di nayntsiker,

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:12.950
un haynt azetike mentshn veynik iz do.

00:20:14.607 --> 00:20:17.843
ir f- ir farshtey- ir farshteyt mir,

00:20:14.840 --> 00:20:16.130
⟨shoyn...⟩

00:20:17.843 --> 00:20:21.980
s'iz do iberlebungen, un haynt layd ikh mer fun ale mol.

00:20:21.980 --> 00:20:27.932
far vos? di froy ligt a ge- zi iz geven a froy, hot ir z- ir zet dokh az...

00:20:28.258 --> 00:20:31.770
un a sheyne un a ⟨z-⟩ gerotene un al...

00:20:31.770 --> 00:20:36.178
ligt, nit zi kon reydn, nit zi kon umgeyn,

00:20:36.178 --> 00:20:42.241
un krekhtset, un s'iz ni- un a h- a heyl⟨bar iz,⟩ me kon ir nit heyln.

00:20:43.918 --> 00:20:48.502
⟨d- ot⟩ hob ikh geha- gebrakht a dokter, hot mir gekost fir hundert shekl, oto do far tsvey vokhn.

00:20:48.745 --> 00:20:50.750
un UNK zi hot,

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:54.790
dos vos mir hobn a mol opgeshport, vos mir hobn a mol getrakht

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:56.686
az mir veln haynt lebn ruik...

00:20:56.811 --> 00:21:01.060
zi krigt oykh pensye, vayle zi hot oykh gearbet a bukhhalter ale yorn...

00:21:01.587 --> 00:21:04.690
az, az, vos mir veln konen lebn gut,

00:21:04.690 --> 00:21:06.900
zaynen mir geblibn faroremt.

00:21:07.577 --> 00:21:09.590
dray yor az zi iz krank,

00:21:09.590 --> 00:21:15.140
dos kost mir tsendliker toyznter. ikh tsol haynt, tsvey toyznt dolar darf ikh tsoln ale monat,

00:21:15.610 --> 00:21:18.780
un oto di vos ikh halt do kost mir oykh toyznt dolar.

00:21:19.542 --> 00:21:22.761
ir farshteyt? dray toyznt dolar fun di gelt

00:21:22.761 --> 00:21:25.040
vos iz, haynt iz dos groshns,

00:21:25.040 --> 00:21:27.449
opgeshport gevorn fun a mol.

00:21:28.182 --> 00:21:31.292
mir hobn dokh nit keyn DOKHODn dokh keyn andere, nor vos,

00:21:31.292 --> 00:21:34.217
ot dos, ikh hob farkoyft UNK ⟨hob ikh⟩ gekoyft do.

00:21:34.980 --> 00:21:37.991
iz haynt klert ir mer ibern krig vi,

00:21:37.991 --> 00:21:40.612
vi frier? ir filt az haynt

00:21:40.740 --> 00:21:42.490
nu, ot haynt fil ikh...

00:21:41.005 --> 00:21:43.310
kumt ales mer tsurik?

00:21:42.760 --> 00:21:45.602
yo, az ikh trakht haynt, trakht ikh,

00:21:45.602 --> 00:21:48.459
az s'kumt oys tsu farkoyfn di shtub, vu vel ikh geyn?

00:21:50.743 --> 00:21:53.853
ir farshteyt? oyf der elter.

00:21:53.853 --> 00:21:59.100
un ikh darf oykh farkoyfn di shtub. far vos? vayl ikh hob nit mit vos tsu haltn di froy.

00:22:00.936 --> 00:22:04.790
bay mir geyen oys ale resursn. ikh hob nokh oyf a monat tsvey,

00:22:04.790 --> 00:22:07.022
oder di resursn geyen oyset.

00:22:07.635 --> 00:22:09.870
un ikh vil do- ikh darf dokh oykh lebn.

00:22:09.870 --> 00:22:12.742
iz ligstu bay nakht un shlofst nit.

00:22:13.407 --> 00:22:17.020
derfar, ⟨i- zo-⟩ ikh zog aykh, ⟨s- ikh,⟩ itster zog ikh aykh,

00:22:15.887 --> 00:22:16.887
⟨iz bay n-...⟩

00:22:17.020 --> 00:22:21.000
ikh lig op nekht un ikh shlof nit un ikh trakht,

00:22:19.730 --> 00:22:21.830
un ir trakht.

00:22:21.422 --> 00:22:23.376
vi azoy zol men aroys.

00:22:23.376 --> 00:22:27.000
un di k⟨i⟩nder umetum kumen, "ABA, ABA,

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:30.400
ABA, do iz finf hundert, do iz hundert." zey hobn nit vos tsu gebn,

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:34.581
vayle zey hobn kinder un zey lebn... oto di o hot gekoyft a shtub, hot zi a,

00:22:34.581 --> 00:22:37.616
a mishkante vos vet ir klekn oyf ir gantsn lebn.

00:22:37.943 --> 00:22:40.380
un di andere hot gor keyn shtub nit.

00:22:40.380 --> 00:22:45.851
iz veyst ir nokh vos? ikh, ikh bin avekgegangen, zi hot mir gemakht HAGRALA oyf erd,

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:50.300
iz zaynen mir ale farshribn zikh. ver gevint? ikh.

00:22:52.506 --> 00:22:55.115
es kumt oys az ikh darf nokh zey boyen.

00:22:56.100 --> 00:22:57.916
ir farshteyt

00:22:58.412 --> 00:22:59.640
vos s'tut zikh?

00:22:59.640 --> 00:23:03.800
iz itster geyt zi un vil farkoyfn di shtub; me darf dokh gelt oyf boyen.

00:23:04.926 --> 00:23:07.380
un gey mit zey lebn mit kinder!

00:23:08.040 --> 00:23:10.960
mayn kharak- mayn kharakter...

00:23:08.301 --> 00:23:10.944
⟨undz vel'mir⟩ bald vayzn ayere kind-...

00:23:10.967 --> 00:23:14.480
ir vet bald, vayzn, undz ayere kinder.

00:23:14.170 --> 00:23:15.590
ot ikh'l aykh...

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:16.749
a groysn shkoyekh aykh.

00:23:16.300 --> 00:23:21.420
nu, TODA RABA. ikh'l aykh zo- ikh hob geredt dos vos ikh hob, keyn helft nit.

00:23:16.871 --> 00:23:17.871
TODA RABA.

00:23:21.470 --> 00:23:22.840
TODA RABA.

00:23:21.930 --> 00:23:23.700
dos iz UNK

00:23:23.700 --> 00:23:27.850
oder dakht zikh mir az ikh hob aykh gegebn materyal, klekt aykh.

00:23:30.525 --> 00:23:34.630
dos iz mayn eltere tokhter D- DANA,

00:23:34.828 --> 00:23:38.540
DANA, velkhe iz geborn gevorn in Vilne,

00:23:38.540 --> 00:23:40.559
gebrakht aher tsu elf yor.

00:23:40.903 --> 00:23:48.720
un dos iz mayn klenere tokhter ORIT, vos iz geborn gevorn do in tsvey vokhn arum vi mir zaynen gekumen in land.

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:53.110
nu, un ikh hob zey a bisl

00:23:53.110 --> 00:23:56.650
ayngeordnt, vifl m- ikh hob gehat meglekhkeyt,

00:23:56.650 --> 00:24:00.877
un haynt zaynen zey tsufridn fun di land un zaynen ⟨fridn⟩ fun lebn.

00:24:01.643 --> 00:24:09.281
UNK ⟨AT YEKHOLA LESAPER LANU AL HAHASHPAA SHEL MA SHEAVAR AL ABA SHELAKH AL HAKHAIM SHELAKH BEETSEM⟩?

00:26:08.458 --> 00:26:14.400
⟨ABA SIPER LAKH AL HAMISHPAKHA SHELO, SHEHAYETA LO?⟩ UNK ⟨MISHPAKHA⟩?

00:26:53.510 --> 00:26:58.190
⟨YESH LAKH EZE MESER? YESH LAKH MASHEHU SHEHAYIT ROTSA LOMAR, SHE-...⟩

00:26:58.190 --> 00:27:04.460
⟨LEGABE HASHOA, LEGABE MA SHEKARA LE- LAHORIM SHELAKH UNK?

00:28:13.134 --> 00:28:14.134
UNK

00:29:05.319 --> 00:29:07.080
⟨HIGATEM LAARETS⟩.

00:29:31.902 --> 00:29:33.550
TODA RABA.

00:29:34.127 --> 00:29:35.730
TODA RABA.
